               <p>THOMAS ROGERS. I lodge in <placeName id="t18310908-209-crimeloc1083">Westminster</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-209-crimeloc1083" type="placeName" value="Westminster"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-209-crimeloc1083" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-209-off1081 t18310908-209-crimeloc1083"></join>. The prisoner lodged in the next bed on the 2nd of September, and the next morning he went away with my shoes - I heard the outside door go, which awoke me; I ran down to the street; I saw a sweep and a boy - I asked if they had met a man; they said Yes, and he had just turned into Orchard-street - the Policeman came by; I told him I had lost my high shoes - he went and got them.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-209-person1568">
                  JOSEPH 
                  CLARK
               <interp inst="t18310908-209-person1568" type="surname" value="CLARK"></interp>
