                     <interp inst="t18310908-209-person1568" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I overtook the prisoner with these shoes.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I get my living by hard labour -I went out that morning at a quarter before five o'clock; I found these shoes outside the door, a few yards off - I took them up; the officer followed me.</p>
